original: Jimmy, feeling famished, set out on a quest to discover a delectable pastry. From dawn to dusk, he scoured for the perfect treat. After hours of searching, he stumbled upon one, only to be met with bitterness upon tasting it. Disheartened, Jimmy departed with a frown, his hunger still lingering.
